item.title: by the time I get to arizona...
item.description: Those are my cousins. of course they are awesome. and I will be hanging out with them tomorrow. it should be fun. I am flying out tonight. I really want to finish my book and start my other book. I want to do that a lot. Tomorrow I am delivering my fathers new site and hanging out with family. it is gunna rule. I am bringing my fancy new shoes.
